The paper deals with solving semantic tasks related to images using deep learning architectures, which is a common theme in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) research. The paper also proposes the incorporation of exemplar-based approaches, which is a technique commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) research. Finally, the paper provides extensive empirical analysis, which is a common theme in information retrieval (cs.IR) research.
